description: Dinner on the table in 15 minutes? Yes please. This quick Mexican-inspired chicken salad is ready in no time.
name: Fast Mexican Chicken Salad Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: In a bowl, toss the coleslaw together with the dressing from the kit, and divide among bowls. Top with chicken and corn, and sprinkle over the crumbled feta from the kit to serve.
